00:15:12,220 --> 00:15:13,800
and then apply medication and heat compress.

298
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:14,740
Okay.

299
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,530
Don't worry.

300
00:15:16,740 --> 00:15:17,420
Hold her.

301
00:15:17,420 --> 00:15:18,200
She sprained her ankle.

302
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:20,930
Good night.

303
00:15:20,930 --> 00:15:21,740
Sleep early.

304
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:22,460
Okay.

305
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:22,960
Bye.

306
00:15:29,820 --> 00:15:30,850
You sprained your ankle?

307
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:31,930
It hurts.

308
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:33,960
Do we still have any medicine at home?

309
00:15:34,580 --> 00:15:35,530
It seems quite serious.

310
00:15:36,340 --> 00:15:37,450
Look at you.

311
00:15:38,940 --> 00:15:42,550
[China Fire and Rescue]

312
00:15:52,820 --> 00:15:55,050
What's with Yu Qilei and Liu Ruyi?

313
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:56,400
I took them out.

314
00:15:56,980 --> 00:15:59,520
Something happened to Yu Qilei’s family.

315
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:00,600
He kept it to himself.

316
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,810
I asked Ruyi to go out and have a drink with him.

317
00:16:02,970 --> 00:16:04,690
Why didn't you tell me?

318
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,440
Weren't you on a mission?

319
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:11,450
How can you just take him out like that?

320
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,570
What if something happens?

321
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,080
I've arranged for someone

322
00:16:18,730 --> 00:16:20,320
to take the shift before going out.

323
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:22,200
Besides,

324
00:16:22,620 --> 00:16:24,210
I have informed Captain Meng about this.

325
00:16:24,610 --> 00:16:25,440
Is there any problem?

326
00:16:26,740 --> 00:16:28,560
When you came back, didn't you promise me

327
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:30,440
not to interfere with my work?

328
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:32,220
You took my people out of the station,

329
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,690
is that not a problem?

330
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:36,080
You're in charge of their work matters.

331
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:39,720
I'm in charge of their mental and physical welfare.

332
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:43,040
Yu is in such a bad state.

333
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:44,320
If we don't sort it out,

334
00:16:44,570 --> 00:16:45,800
it'll become a huge problem in the future.

335
00:16:47,340 --> 00:16:48,920
He should handle his family matters at home,

336
00:16:49,820 --> 00:16:51,330
not bring them to work.

337
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:54,000
I know nothing about Yu Qilei’s family.

338
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:56,650
But it can’t be an excuse for him to affect his work.

339
00:16:57,740 --> 00:16:59,140
He's an experienced firefighter now.

340
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:00,240
What can't he handle?

341
00:17:04,980 --> 00:17:05,850
Look at you.

342
00:17:06,260 --> 00:17:08,330
It's easy for you to say.

343
00:17:09,380 --> 00:17:10,520
We firefighters

344
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:12,530
barely have two days off a year.

345
00:17:12,980 --> 00:17:15,560
We spend most of our time here at the station.

346
00:17:16,290 --> 00:17:17,180
He spends way more time

347
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:19,730
with us than with his family.

348
00:17:20,180 --> 00:17:20,700
Tell me,

349
00:17:20,700 --> 00:17:21,810
can you ignore

350
00:17:22,220 --> 00:17:23,250
your buddy when he has a problem?

351
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:24,730
Can we ignore it?

352
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:26,960
You treat this place as a unit,

353
00:17:27,540 --> 00:17:29,880
but we treat it as our home.

354
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:38,120
Since we've chosen the firefighting career,

355
00:17:38,660 --> 00:17:39,720
sacrifice is inevitable.

356
00:17:40,420 --> 00:17:41,400
It's normal.

357
00:17:42,540 --> 00:17:43,500
I also made sacrifices.

358
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,250
What's wrong with that?

359
00:17:44,940 --> 00:17:46,280
And I think it's worth it.

360
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:47,720
It's necessary.

361
00:17:52,180 --> 00:17:53,490
How should I put it?

362
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:56,360
I used to

363
00:17:57,300 --> 00:17:58,530
have the same thought.

364
00:17:59,540 --> 00:18:00,160
Indeed.

365
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:03,120
But after I became an instructor,

366
00:18:03,970 --> 00:18:05,000
I changed my mind.

367
00:18:06,140 --> 00:18:07,700
You can't hold everyone

368
00:18:07,700 --> 00:18:08,850
up to your own standards.

369
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:11,770
Fire rescue is an ambition

370
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:12,850
for you and me.

371
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:15,410
But to many people,

372
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:17,250
it's just a job.

373
00:18:18,260 --> 00:18:20,180
Maybe some people joined

374
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:21,890
for the stability of an establishment.

375
00:18:22,740 --> 00:18:23,530
But

376
00:18:24,260 --> 00:18:25,600
they train just like us.

377
00:18:26,450 --> 00:18:27,060
During missions,

378
00:18:27,060 --> 00:18:29,080
they rush into the fire just like us.

379
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:30,730
What's wrong with that?

380
00:18:31,420 --> 00:18:32,480
Do you think they're wrong?

381
00:18:33,260 --> 00:18:33,800
Right?

382
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:34,980
What right do you have

383
00:18:34,980 --> 00:18:36,720
to expect everyone to be like you?

384
00:18:42,700 --> 00:18:43,140
I'm done talking to you.

385
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:43,800
Go to sleep.

386
00:18:53,970 --> 00:18:55,090
In the next two days,

387
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:57,880
I plan to hold a Family Open House Day at the station

388
00:18:58,700 --> 00:19:01,570
to bring the family members of our station mates here

389
00:19:02,180 --> 00:19:03,120
and gather together.

390
00:19:03,780 --> 00:19:04,730
I refuse.

391
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:06,050
I don't have time.

392
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:10,320
It's never a waste of time to prepare.

393
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:13,000
I don't agree.

394
00:19:13,900 --> 00:19:15,800
The firefighting competition hasn't been settled yet.

395
00:19:16,180 --> 00:19:17,420
There are so many problems at the station.

396
00:19:17,420 --> 00:19:19,410
I don't have time for your open house day.

397
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:24,360
Fine.

398
00:19:24,980 --> 00:19:26,080
You can keep your opinion.

399
00:19:26,700 --> 00:19:29,000
