448
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:21,700
First,

449
00:21:22,370 --> 00:21:23,500
during the open house day,

450
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:25,140
we can't delay our

451
00:21:25,140 --> 00:21:26,400
daily training and tasks.

452
00:21:27,070 --> 00:21:27,660
Second,

453
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:29,300
the one who suggested it

454
00:21:29,300 --> 00:21:30,220
