459
00:21:47,780 --> 00:21:51,050
Go back and make your preparations.

460
00:21:51,730 --> 00:21:52,820
As for the specific date,

461
00:21:52,990 --> 00:21:55,460
I'll update everyone once it's confirmed.

462
00:21:56,390 --> 00:21:57,140
Any questions?

463
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:58,280
No.

464
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:58,870
Okay.

465
00:21:58,870 --> 00:21:59,580
Dismissed.

466
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:00,170
Attention!

467
00:22:01,010 --> 00:22:01,640
Back to your classes.

468
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,360
Yu, a word, please.

469
00:22:05,120 --> 00:22:06,220
Everyone from class one,

470
00:22:06,220 --> 00:22:07,310
march off!

471
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,160
Take this opportunity to

472
00:22:09,490 --> 00:22:10,960
take Milan and Miaomiao here.

473
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:13,100
