474
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:14,620
This is a rare opportunity.

475
00:22:14,620 --> 00:22:15,290
Hurry up.

476
00:22:15,290 --> 00:22:15,790
Go.

477
00:22:15,790 --> 00:22:16,210
All the best.

478
00:22:16,210 --> 00:22:16,800
Okay.

