00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,570
at work.

487
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:30,660
Yes.

488
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:31,630
Really?

489
00:22:32,260 --> 00:22:32,840
Okay.

490
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:34,360
Pass the phone to your mother.

491
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:35,450
Mom.

492
00:22:35,450 --> 00:22:36,200
Dad said

493
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:38,180
we could visit him at work.

494
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:39,690
Miaomiao has school

495
00:22:39,690 --> 00:22:40,610
and I have work.

496
00:22:41,120 --> 00:22:41,790
How?

497
00:22:42,020 --> 00:22:43,260
Take a leave.

498
00:22:43,890 --> 00:22:45,860
