504
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:54,890
All right, I'm hanging up.

505
00:22:54,890 --> 00:22:55,730
I have something to do.

506
00:23:12,870 --> 00:23:14,300
[Clinic]

507
00:23:14,300 --> 00:23:15,260
Pain is inevitable.
[Clinic]

508
00:23:15,260 --> 00:23:15,510
[Clinic]

509
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:17,360
