519
00:23:35,210 --> 00:23:36,770
What should we do now?

520
00:23:37,060 --> 00:23:37,770
Take the medicine.

521
00:23:37,770 --> 00:23:38,660
Ice compress.

522
00:23:38,660 --> 00:23:39,870
Have a good rest.

523
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:53,060
Nan Chu.

524
00:23:53,060 --> 00:23:53,900
