546
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:38,720
It's okay.

547
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:39,890
We can wait.

548
00:24:40,270 --> 00:24:41,050
Well,

549
00:24:41,460 --> 00:24:44,490
